From d62c638e642388df9c522a6fbe209f56006eeeb9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: DJPieter81 <pieter@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 5 Apr 2026 15:01:04 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] EV player: fix 5 engine bugs + tune midrange/combo profiles
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Engine fixes (permanent):
- Psychic Frog: permanent +1/+1 counters (was temp mods that reset EOT)
- Psychic Frog: smart discard heuristic (protect removal/counters,
  discard excess lands/dupes/uncastable, aggressive when pumped)
- Psychic Frog: combat damage draw trigger (draw a card on player damage)
- Living End: cycling now handled in EVPlayer decision loop
  (was filtered out by can_cast check — 0 cycles/game → 3.9/game)
- Burn targeting: factor creature clock for 5+ power targets
- match_playbyplay.html: fix duplicate return/closing brace (JS syntax error)

AI decision fixes:
- Counter burn threat increased (1.0x → 1.5x face damage threat value)
- Holdback disabled when opponent has no clock (opp_clock >= 10)
- Survival bonuses scaled by opponent creature power
- Storm mulligan: require cost reducer in 7-card hands
- Aggro closing speed: lower attack threshold when opponent <= 10 life

Midrange profile tuning:
- high_power_creature_bonus: 0 → 3 (Murktide priority)
- on_curve_creature_bonus: 2 → 3 (deploy on curve)
- discard_early_bonus: 4 → 5 (T1 Thoughtseize priority)
- survival_removal_bonus: 6 → 7
- pass_threshold: -5 → -3

Results (300 games/matchup):
- 6/9 matchups within ±5pp of expected (was 0/9)
- Living End functional (3.9 cycles, 1.4 cascades/game)
- Frog attacks 7x more, avg power 1.5 (was 1.2)
